                        short initTransferLength)
Constructor to create a ReadRequestState instance, which creates a request to the iSCSI Target.

Parameters:
initConnection - This is the connection, which is used for the network transmission.
initBuffer - This buffer should be read.
initTaskAttributes - The task attributes of this task.
initExpectedDataTransferLength - The expected length in bytes, which should be transfered.
initLogicalBlockAddress - The logical block address of the first block to read.
initTransferLength - The number of blocks to read.
